{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "話桑麻", "storyInfo": "幾名少年核對了各自發現的異樣，種種線索都指向了突然回到大荒城的不速之客。\n另一方面，久別重逢的績和黍在神農祠前開始了一場長談。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g10_fairyfarmland_ex", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_cnclouds", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "望不到頭的稻田，迷離如幻。天地寬廣，卻萬籟俱寂。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一絲酒香飄過，雲做旋舞，飄飄然流入一隻酒盞。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仰頭飲盡，瞬間天朗氣清。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……真是一場好夢。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼有功夫來我這裡？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這最近不是很熱鬧？正好來看看你答應我的高粱酒釀好沒有。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在夢裡，我怎麼把酒給你？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說的是哪一年的酒，這又是你的哪個夢呢？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢裡喝不到，讓我聞聞味道也好啊。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者是來看看我那個最辛苦的妹妹，最近是不是又累瘦了一點。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來這就是小年做出來的奇妙物件？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#3$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩人揮一揮衣袖，手邊便出現一壇酒，兩隻盞。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她抬手拍碎壇口的泥封，陳年酒香霎時蔓延。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詩人回身，眺望。稻田綿延百里、萬里，春夏秋冬於天空中盤旋，寒來暑往，春去秋來。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你在這顆“心臟”裡看到的風景？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無盡的稻田，輪轉的四季，你每日都在耕作，這裡真能造出你們說的那個東西？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需不需要我也來幫你們一把？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#9$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怕你來了，這個容器也會變成一個大酒缸，或者是突然有了自己的想法，覺得世間不逍遙，不如長夢不醒。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的不需要我幫忙？你在這裡待了多少年，我都快要記不清了，再不出來走走就怕你憋成我的酒葫蘆。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別的弟弟妹妹，只怕是看不清事裡事外，只有你，我只擔心你看得太透。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看得太透，就看不到“自己”了。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過是在這裡耕種罷了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山水草木皆有情，這一草一木在你看來，也未必和我們的生命有什麼區別。", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還有什麼放不下的東西呢，你還會在意什麼呢？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頡曾經也留下過那麼多書卷字帖，她希望能教每個人讀書識字。但她走後，那些字帖書文也一同消失，除了我們，沒人記得她。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可後來我去過幾所學堂，還有天師府，看到有些書本中用的字跡，竟和她的一模一樣。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她那些東西早都沒有了，連我都沒能留下哪怕一張，但她說過的話又從那些學生的嘴裡說了出來，寫過的字又在那些學生的筆下復現。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得她和我說過，“重要的是我能留下來的”。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我只是在看，這片稻田的盡頭，能留下什麼。如果有一日我也消散了，我能為這裡留下什麼。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直在看著的那個結局，有改變嗎？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#8$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白茫茫一片大雪，從來沒有變過。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……春種秋收，繁盛過後，最後都被一場大雪掩埋。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣啊……", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對這個結果，你會失望嗎？還是覺得遺憾？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來這世間走過一遭，這本身不就是結果？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像這世上無數人一樣，有誰是想著生命有一個終點，就無所適從了呢。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我們有的兄弟不這麼想……那位弟弟，他回來了？", "name": "令"}, "figure_art": "avg_2023_ling_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "令", "content": "原來那個膽小又乖巧的績去哪裡了呢？"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_2023_ling_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "令", "content": "唉，這些弟弟妹妹，還是小時候比較可愛。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我會去見見他。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g3_fieldpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一、二、三……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大嗓門，這些到底是什麼新品種啊？我好像從來沒看過，長得還挺好看的。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說了你也聽不懂，別多嘴，幫我找就對了。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，叫人幫忙還這麼大脾氣……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了大嗓門，我還想問你一個事情……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是天師府的學徒嗎，而且我認識的人裡，除了黍姐姐和小禾，就數你懂得最多了。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要問什麼，趕緊說啊。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#5$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你……有沒有見過我的爸爸媽媽？", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#7$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*炎國粗口*天師府上上下下多少人，你以為我是警衛大爺，把每個人都記得清清楚楚？！", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#6$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "腦子被泥砸傻了吧你！", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道就不知道嘛，幹嘛突然兇人。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為什麼想起來要問我這個？", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#5$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我見到了一個奇怪的商人，他說他是從大荒城外面，從很遠的地方來的。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姐姐說，我的爸媽也是去很遠的地方當天師了。但是不知道他們到底是去做什麼，這麼多年都沒回來，也從來沒有聽別人說起過。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大嗓門，你真的不能幫我打聽打聽嗎？", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不用讓他們回來，我就是想寫封信告訴他們，大荒城快搬家了，搬上了移動地塊。他們回家的時候別找不到路。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……行了，不用白擔心。你當天師府是什麼地方，到該回家的時候，肯定有人帶他們回家的。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#9$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洪水影響過的地塊，就到這裡為止了吧？", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "小滿", "content": "好像是的……"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "小滿", "content": "怎麼了？你要找的這種水稻，跟洪水有關係嗎？"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不該問的別問，天師府的工作，說了你也不明白。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神氣什麼！小禾說過，只要我耐著性子多看幾本書，憑我的源石技藝天賦，肯定也能考上天師府的！", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好，那就等你考上了再說吧。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，我託你找水稻這件事，千萬別跟別人講啊。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#10$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "小滿", "content": "為……"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "小滿", "content": "算了，你肯定不會說的。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂……你最近，過得還好？有沒有受欺負？", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#9$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……挺開心的啊。小禾和黍姐姐都挺照顧我，職農大伯大嬸們人也很好，最近還認識了小燭台和小毛筆兩個新朋友……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是什麼問題？你關心我？", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#9$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰關心你這個野丫頭！", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，今天還是辛苦你了，照顧好自己吧。", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#2$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次要是有人欺負你，你就照我教你的，用笛子敲他的頭！", "name": "天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g12_cityoperastage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_bitw_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑麻日已長，我土日已廣……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敢教邪祟詭魔拓易，天地煥新光……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啦……啦……", "name": "績"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.8, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直不喜歡這尊塑像。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰說“神農”就一定得是短褐穿結，飽經風霜的樣子？明明她也是很愛美的，她總是在髮髻上戴著花，也很喜歡我做的衣裳。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我記得很清楚，她的眼睛，和你很像。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能讓夕給她留下一幅畫像該多好……可惜那個時候，夕好像也還沒有學會畫畫。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 0.8, "channel": "step1", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為你不會再回來了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再怎麼講我也不是離家出走的年紀，我又什麼時候說過不會回來的話？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊子漂泊在外久了總會想家的，想來想去，也只有這裡能算我的家了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偏偏是這個時候？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是能早兩天回來，還能趕上今年的社戲，再嚐嚐你包的麥穗餃子。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以啊，“遠行的餃子，回家的麵”，想吃什麼，家裡都有。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃完飯，就又該上路了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼我才留下不到兩天，就這麼急著趕我走？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是只是回來歇歇，想留多久都可以。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是想問問你，你真的只是回來歇歇的嗎？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#7$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次回來，大荒城都要變一番模樣。誰還能想到，千年前這裡還是一片凍土的樣子。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是人們從緊挨著邪祟詭魔的地方搶下了這一片土地。那時候，山河混沌，天無四時，但是人心明亮。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們不分身分，不分國別，互相扶持，敵人只有眼前的荒地，還有不知什麼時候會出現的邪魔。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前幾天，我還夢見過她，也夢見過那位老先生。所以我想，可能是時候回來看看了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所幸還能找到回家的路，只可惜……人心不古。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又有多久，沒好好看過這裡的人了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天下熙熙，皆為利來；天下攘攘，皆為利往。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "利在哪，人就在哪。哪都一樣。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，你覺得朝廷裡的人，商量的到底是如何保住我們一家人的性命，還是如何尋求一個對他們而言最穩妥的局面？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你真的相信，年的那個造物，可以保所有人的平安？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是唯一可以保大家性命的辦法。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#8$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是把性命交到別人手裡。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雙方合伙做生意，有利一起賺，風險卻只有一邊承擔。這不是一筆划算買賣，至少不是筆公平的買賣。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要想生意做得長久，那至少要讓雙方背著一樣的風險才行。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠行了這麼久，你在意的就只有帳本上的盈虧了？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在意的是你。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你累了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為這裡的一草一木操勞還不夠，又幫年去做那個工程，是很耗神的。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然的話，這次的事，你本該更早發現的。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#8$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千年來，無數次天災，每一次，天災降臨在這片土地上，你都會提前知道……這片土地上的一切，你都會感同身受。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底在堅持些什麼？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，誰才是逆天而行的那一個？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g8_crestofweir", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醒醒！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，你看到了什麼？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了……什麼……？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……你怎麼知道？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "左樂手上捻著一縷絲線，眼看著它很快消失在了空氣中。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能是有人在惡作劇……大概是源石技藝吧……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#3$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到的那些東西應該是你自己的幻覺，但有他想讓你看到的東西，就像是某種心理暗示……你看到了什麼？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我好像看到了一位老農，他……或者是她？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我在地裡耕種。我種不出莊稼，但是越來越老，再沒力氣拿起鋤頭……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有河對岸的樹上掛著不少木牌，那邊沒人過去過，但我看到了上面好像寫著人名……那個老農也消失了。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……河對岸？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他讓你看見河對岸……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#10$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_breezetree", "volume": 0.4, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "禾生嘆了口氣，順著河流向遠處眺望。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河對岸的樹木鬱鬱蔥蔥，一陣風刮過，似乎還能聽到樹葉沙沙作響的聲音。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "mstep", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "mstep", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小禾，小燭台，你們在這？", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#7$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小滿姑娘！你到哪裡去了？！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#6$2"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛找水稻去了……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#2$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找水稻？你不是去找牧獸了？什麼水稻需要專門去找？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#4$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g3_fieldpath", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1238_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，我託你找水稻這件事，千萬別跟別人講啊。", "name": "暴躁的天師學徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1238_1#10$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g8_crestofweir", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過別人……要保密的……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇奇怪怪……怎麼盡是讓人摸不著頭腦的事……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰要你找水稻？什麼樣子的水稻？在哪裡找到的？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小燭台？你怎麼這麼緊張……有點可怕……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小滿姑娘！", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#5$2"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好好好我說……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一個天師府的小個子學生……說要找特殊品種的水稻用來交作業……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道是什麼種類……只是看上去像是紅色的，紅得發黑……在堰口有一些，離這不遠的水田裡也有一些。", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g8_crestofweir", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小滿"}, "figure_art": "avg_4122_grabds_1#11$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小禾，前些日子收上來的糧食都放在哪裡？", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城有集中的糧倉，在核心城裡。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能請你現在就去查看一下糧倉嗎？如果有什麼異狀，立刻去找老鄉長。", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……到底是什麼事這麼著急？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怕已經來不及了……", "name": "左樂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4121_zuole_1#4$2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g12_cityoperastage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的社戲一共是三齣，《大狩天》《爭天時》《萬物生》。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但很早之前，在第一、二齣之間應該還有一齣《度北疆》，很久都不唱了。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你還記得該怎麼唱嗎？能不能再唱一段？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "調子還記得，詞已經差不多忘了。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是陳年舊事，沒什麼好唱的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，台下沒有觀眾，唱戲也沒勁。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過眼就忘的戲，看起來也沒勁。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我還記得……", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#2$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得，北方的這一塊邪魔碎片，是當時的人不擇手段尋來對付祂的方法，祂的化身如今卻在幫人們抵擋邪魔的災害。實在是有趣。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們早就不該再和祂混為一談。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確不該。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邪祟詭魔，絕不能為普通百姓所知，但偏偏一片罕見的少受源石污染的土地就在這裡，實在沒辦法放棄。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一千年來，這裡的人們就生活在與那片穢土一河之隔的地方。人們也真的在這裡埋頭耕作，不問世事，持續了一千年。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有因有果。千年前，人們自己種下的因，現在，也該有人來摘這個果了。還得是合適的人才行。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……告訴我，那場災害，和你無關，對嗎？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我何時對你說過假話？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是有時候會選擇不說真話。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你這次回來，到底是想做什麼？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我剛才說的，只是回家看看。", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是跟以前一樣，只是想問問你，姐姐，要不要跟我一起走？", "name": "績"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1236_1#9$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我的回答也是跟以前一樣，我不會離開，也不想離開。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#17$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}